Function find_all_connected_components(G):
V ← G.nodes, V' ← empty set, K ← 1
result ← List()
while V’ != V:
select s from V - V’
add s to V’
Q ← "{s"}, C_K ← "{s"}
while Q is not empty:
u ← Q.dequeue()
for each v in u’s neighbors:
if v is not in V’:
add v to V’, Q.enqueue(v), add v to C_K
add C_K to result
K ← K + 1
return K - 1
